	<!-- EN: #2/3 Tiny army study report -->
    <AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.label>#2/3 粘土人偶研究報告</AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.label>
    <!--
        EN: Replicative properties of the Clay figure\n\nAbstract:\nThis report details observations concerning the recently found replicative properties of the Clay figure. After some time of inactivity, the object spontaneously created another similar figurine, which was somewhat different in shape but still reminiscent of the previous figurine. The newly created object seems to have the same properties as the original, which might also include it's ability to replicate. The only notable difference is that the copy seems to be weighing less. No other notable properties were observed.\n\nObservations:\nThe object is able to make imperfect copies of itself.\n\nDiscussion:\nIf this is the only anomalous property of the object, then no risk should be associated with it, this, however, should be proven first.\n\nRecommendations:\nFurther research
    -->
	<AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.text>粘土人偶的複製行爲\n\n摘要：\n本報告詳細記錄了關於近期發現的人偶的複製性質的觀察結果。在一段時間的靜止之後，該物體自發地創造了另一個類似的人偶，其形狀略有不同，但仍然讓人聯想到之前的雕像。新的物體似乎具有與原物體相同的性質，這可能也包括其複製的能力。唯一顯著的區別是複製品似乎重量更輕。沒有觀察到其他顯著的性質。\n\n現象：\n該物體能夠製造自身的非完美複製品。\n\n討論：\n如果這是物體的唯一異常性質，那麼不應該將它與任何風險關聯起來，然而，此推斷應該首先得到證實。\n\n建議：\n繼續研究。</AE_Replicator.comps.CompAEStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.text>
	
